  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the <span class=\"italic \">xy</span>-plane, a line has a slope of 6 and passes through the point <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"with coordinates zero comma 8\"></span></span>. Which of the following is an equation of this line?</p>\n",
